title: Lithuania Tourist Arrivals
description: Tourist Arrivals in Lithuania increased to 567.40 Thousand in the second quarter of 2022 from 305.50 Thousand in the first quarter of 2022. Tourist Arrivals in Lithuania averaged 339.76 Thousand from 2007 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 666.50 Thousand in the third quarter of 2018 and a record low of 75.10 Thousand in the first quarter of 2021. This page provides - Lithuania Tourist Arrivals- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistics Lithuania
